{"tid":948219,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫管局去年度赤字8.4億 行政總裁再加人工年薪破600萬","createTime":"2018-12-20T01:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T03:35:23.000Z","uid":136252,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1d6c3fac82f6352bfe613b1c65350ffd80e53474","tid":948219,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T01:18:02.000Z","msg":"醫院管理局今日向立法會提交2017/18年度年報，當局全年虧蝕較2016-17年度的15億虧蝕大減至8.4億，連續2年出現赤字。不過醫管局5名管理層就繼續錄得輕微升幅，當中政總裁梁栢賢獲支薪601.8萬港元，較再上年度多2.3萬，5名高層薪金達2,700多萬，亦較再上一年度微升。<br />\n<br />\n據醫管局年報顯示，2017/18年度支出達641.8億，較上一年度多31億，當中員工成本支出佔最多達451億港元，而藥物、維修、設備等開支均有增加，在扣除633億收入後，全年虧蝕為8.4億。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181212/59020915\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F59020915&d=bxRmApblJ2GFsDTLoFA1i1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=112188a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F59020915&h=a8cd9a4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181212/59020915</a>"},{"pid":"64e9371be9d8d37e834c336b14014426bd7b24f0","tid":948219,"uid":28599,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T01:25:03.000Z","msg":"排隊排長龍<br />\n醫療事故一年10幾單<br />\n高層就年年加人工<br />\n同狗鐵一鳩樣"},{"pid":"81cf44f8c575be393f540fdd1b60d3a7384d0965","tid":948219,"uid":61954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T01:31:32.000Z","msg":"肥上瘦下"},{"pid":"8d0399367c03ac4cce6b2d70a1ebda84d66d238e","tid":948219,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T01:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  高層正仆街"},{"pid":"3a8ae34d908f4dc7f5614b1c7691a7fef20fbccc","tid":948219,"uid":198506,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T01:32:55.000Z","msg":"都慣啦。。。間間大機構都係咁。。。可憐低下層<img sr